'''Kevin Pollack''' (born [[October 30]], [[1950s#1957|1957]]) provided a voice for ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]''. He also played such roles as one of the [[Brownie]]s in [[George Lucas]]'s [[Willow (film)|''Willow'']] and has been in such movies as ''The Usual Suspects'' and ''The Whole Nine Yards''.

